            <h2 class="splashPanel__title" id="what-are-mortgage-interest-rates">What are mortgage interest rates?</h2>
            <div class="rich-text-container" role="region" aria-label="Rich text undefined">
              <p class="richTextElement">Mortgage interest rates decide how much you’ll need to pay when you get a mortgage.

              </p>
              <p class="richTextElement">The interest rate will affect how much you pay towards your mortgage each month. The higher the interest rate, the more you’ll pay every month.</p>
              <p class="richTextElement">Mortgage rates, like most interest rates in the UK, relate to the 
                <a href="#">Bank of England base rate</a>.
              </p>
              <p class="richTextElement">If the base rate goes up, interest rates usually go up by a similar amount. If the base rate goes down, interest rates usually go down.</p>
            </div>
