            <div class="rich-text-container" role="region" aria-label="Rich text undefined">
              <p class="richTextElement">The recent outbreak of coronavirus (Covid-19) has had widespread impact on the economy.</p>
              <p class="richTextElement">The Bank of England cut the base rate twice in an emergency decision in March. First from 0.75% to 0.25% on 11 March 2020 and again on the 19 March 2020. </p>
