          <div class="rich-text-container" role="region" aria-label="Rich text undefined">
            <p class="richTextElement">Remortgaging can save you money if you're able to find a better deal. </p>
            <p class="richTextElement">But there may be fees to pay if you're moving to a different lender. So it's worth making sure the fees do not outweigh the remortgage savings. </p>
