        <h2 class="splashPanel__title" id="how-many-mortgage-deals-are-there">How many mortgage deals are there?</h2>
        <div class="rich-text-container" role="region" aria-label="Rich text undefined">
          <p class="richTextElement">It’s hard to know exactly how many mortgage deals there are.</p>
          <p class="richTextElement">This is because lenders often add and remove mortgage deals from the market. Sometimes lenders stop offering mortgages completely.</p>
          <p class="richTextElement">Many lenders have reduced their range of mortgages because of the coronavirus pandemic, too.</p>
          <p class="richTextElement">Right now, based on our own data for April 2021, there are around 19,000 different mortgages offered by lenders that we have access to.</p>
          <p class="richTextElement">Before the pandemic, that number was around 45,000.</p>
